\begin_layout Theorem
设
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{T}=\left(0,l\right)\times\left(0,T\right]$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\varGamma_{T}=\overline{Q_{T}}/Q_{T}$
\end_inset

