\begin_layout Subsubsection
混合型边界
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们注意到，有界区间问题是有两个边界
\begin_inset Formula $x=0,x=l$
\end_inset

的。混合型边界指的是两个边界不是同一类型的边界，比如一个是Dirichlet边界一个是Robin边界。在此仅举一例：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
u_{tt}=c^{2}u_{xx}\\
u\left(x,0\right)=\varphi\left(x\right)\\
u_{t}\left(x,0\right)=\psi\left(x\right)\\
u\left(0,t\right)=u_{x}\left(l,t\right)+a_{l}u\left(l,t\right)=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
0<x<l,t>0\\
0<x<l\\
0<x<l\\
(\text{混\text{合}}\text{边\text{界}})
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
处理这类问题我们就不再使用9.1.3中介绍的换元法了，可以直接用变量分离法。与之前不同的地方只有边值不同而已。与前面类似，为了满足
\begin_inset Formula $u\left(0,t\right)=u_{x}\left(l,t\right)+a_{l}u\left(l,t\right)=0$
\end_inset

，我们有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
X^{\prime\prime}+\lambda X=0\\
X\left(0\right)=X^{\prime}\left(l\right)+a_{l}X\left(l\right)=0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这个问题的特征值和特征函数就没那么简单了。此时Strum-Liouville边值定理依旧成立，即
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda>0$
\end_inset

,从而方程
\begin_inset Formula $X^{\prime\prime}+\lambda X=0$
\end_inset

的解为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
X=Acos\sqrt{\lambda}x+Bsin\sqrt{\lambda}x
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
那么代入
\begin_inset Formula $X\left(0\right)=X^{\prime}\left(l\right)+a_{l}X\left(l\right)=0$
\end_inset

，就有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
A=0\\
\sqrt{\lambda}Bcos\sqrt{\lambda}l+a_{l}Bsin\sqrt{\lambda}l=0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
特征值要满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\sqrt{\lambda}=-a_{l}tan\sqrt{\lambda}l
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
实际上当
\begin_inset Formula $a_{l}>0$
\end_inset

时，有无穷多个根（图解法），我们设为
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{n}$
\end_inset

这是已知的，我们不能直接求出显式的
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{n}$
\end_inset

，所以把它保留就好了。后面的步骤与前面完全相同不再赘述。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Robin边界
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Robin边界对应的特征值问题是
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
X^{\prime\prime}+\lambda X=0\\
X^{\prime}\left(0\right)-a_{0}X\left(0\right)=X^{\prime}\left(l\right)+a_{l}X\left(l\right)=0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Robin边界问题相对来讲要复杂地多，因为Strum-Liouville边值定理不一定成立，那么其特征值和特征函数往往表示很复杂或者比较难去求得。往往需要分类讨
论。这种边界条件有十几种.在此仅作简要讨论。方程
\begin_inset Formula $X^{\prime\prime}+\lambda X=0$
\end_inset

的通解是
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
X=Acos\sqrt{\lambda}x+Bsin\sqrt{\lambda}x\\
X=Ax+B\\
X=Acosh\sqrt{-\lambda}x+Bsinh\sqrt{-\lambda}x
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
\lambda>0\\
\lambda=0\\
\lambda<0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
那么
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
X^{\prime}=-\sqrt{\lambda}Asin\sqrt{\lambda}x+\sqrt{\lambda}Bcos\sqrt{\lambda}x\\
X^{\prime}=A\\
X^{\prime}=\sqrt{-\lambda}Asinh\sqrt{-\lambda}x+\sqrt{-\lambda}Bcosh\sqrt{-\lambda}x
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
\lambda>0\\
\lambda=0\\
\lambda<0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
代入边值条件，
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda=0$
\end_inset

是特征值当且仅当
\begin_inset Formula $a_{0}+a_{l}\left(a_{0}l+1\right)=0$
\end_inset

是显然的，另外地，我们更关心的是
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda>0$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda<0$
\end_inset

时的情况，先来看
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda>0$
\end_inset

时：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{\lambda}B-a_{0}A=0\\
-\sqrt{\lambda}Asin\sqrt{\lambda}l+\sqrt{\lambda}Bcos\sqrt{\lambda}l+a_{l}\left(Acos\sqrt{\lambda}l+Bsin\sqrt{\lambda}l\right)=0
\end{array} & \lambda>0\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这要求
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
a_{0}\left(\sqrt{\lambda}cos\sqrt{\lambda}l+a_{l}sin\sqrt{\lambda}l\right)+\sqrt{\lambda}\left(-\sqrt{\lambda}sin\sqrt{\lambda}l+a_{l}cos\sqrt{\lambda}l\right)=0
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
为了简化，让
\begin_inset Formula $\omega=\sqrt{\lambda}$
\end_inset

，则（10.32）即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
tan\omega l=\frac{\omega\left(a_{0}+a_{l}\right)}{\omega^{2}-a_{0}a_{l}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
再运用图解法分类讨论即可（求导可帮助判断）。再看看
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda<0$
\end_inset

时的情况：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{-\lambda}B-a_{0}A=0\\
\sqrt{-\lambda}Asinh\sqrt{-\lambda}l+\sqrt{-\lambda}Bcosh\sqrt{-\lambda}l+a_{l}\left(Acosh\sqrt{-\lambda}l+Bsinh\sqrt{-\lambda}l\right)=0
\end{array} & \lambda<0\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
让
\begin_inset Formula $\omega=\sqrt{-\lambda}$
\end_inset

,就有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\omega\left(\omega sinh\omega l+a_{l}cosh\omega l\right)+a_{0}\left(\omega cosh\omega l+a_{l}sinh\omega l\right)=0
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这要求
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
tanh\omega l=\frac{-\omega\left(a_{0}+a_{l}\right)}{\omega^{2}+a_{0}a_{l}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
再用图解法，分类讨论即可。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
热方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Dirichlet边界
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
来看热方程的Dirichlet边值问题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
u_{t}=ku_{xx}\\
u\left(x,0\right)=\phi\left(x\right)\\
u\left(0,t\right)=u\left(l,t\right)=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
0<x<l,t>0\\
0<x<l\\
(Dirichlet\text{边\text{界}})
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
完全是依葫芦画瓢，假设方程
\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}=ku_{xx}$
\end_inset

具有分离解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
u=X\left(x\right)T\left(t\right)
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
代入得到
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
XT^{\prime}=c^{2}X^{\prime\prime}T
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{T^{\prime}}{c^{2}T}=\frac{X^{\prime\prime}}{X}=-\lambda
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
边界上，为了满足
\begin_inset Formula $u\left(0,t\right)=u\left(l,t\right)=0$
\end_inset

，我们有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
X^{\prime\prime}+\lambda X=0\\
X\left(0\right)=X\left(l\right)=0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求出特征值
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{n}=\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}$
\end_inset

，特征函数为
\begin_inset Formula $X_{n}=sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x$
\end_inset

，由Strum-Liouville边值定理，函数系
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ X_{n}\right\} $
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $0<x<l$
\end_inset

上完备，由（10.15）我们还能得到
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
T^{\prime}+c^{2}\lambda T=0
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注意这是与以往不同的地方！把
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{n}=\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}$
\end_inset

代入，就有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
T=C_{n}e^{-\left(\frac{cn\pi}{l}\right)^{2}t}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
于是
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
u=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}X_{n}\left(x\right)T_{n}\left(t\right)=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}C_{n}e^{-\left(\frac{cn\pi}{l}\right)^{2}t}sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们通过控制常数
\begin_inset Formula $C_{n}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $D_{n}$
\end_inset

来使得
\begin_inset Formula $u=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}X_{n}\left(x\right)T_{n}\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

满足初值
\begin_inset Formula $u\left(x,0\right)=\phi\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

。把初值代入我们需要
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
u\left(x,0\right)=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}C_{n}sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x=\phi\left(x\right)
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
只要让
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
C_{n}=\frac{2}{l}\int_{0}^{l}\phi\left(s\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}sds
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
即可，于是我们有最终的广义解：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
u=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}X_{n}\left(x\right)T_{n}\left(t\right)=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}\left(\frac{2}{l}\int_{0}^{l}\phi\left(s\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}sds\right)e^{-\left(\frac{cn\pi}{l}\right)^{2}t}sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
其它
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
热方程的其它边界情况处理方法于波动方程类似。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
非齐次边界的处理方法
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
非齐次这个词我们依旧很熟悉了，对于不齐次的三种边界，我们都是采用构造辅助函数，利用叠加原理去解决。先来看Dirichlet边界：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
u\left(0,t\right)=f\left(t\right)\\
u\left(l,t\right)=g\left(t\right)
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
构造辅助函数，把边界给齐次化。设
\begin_inset Formula $u=v+h$
\end_inset

，我们假设
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

是满足齐次化边界的，来看看辅助函数
\begin_inset Formula $h$
\end_inset

如果是关于x的一次函数
\begin_inset Formula $h=Ax+B$
\end_inset

，系数要满足什么条件。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
u\left(0,t\right)=f\left(t\right)=B\\
u\left(l,t\right)=g\left(t\right)=Al+B
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
很容易求出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
A=\frac{g\left(t\right)-f\left(t\right)}{l}\\
B=f\left(t\right)
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这样，我们可以求出
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

以后再加上
\begin_inset Formula $h=Ax+B$
\end_inset

得到答案
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

，Neumann边界则是用二次函数，Robin边界则也是一次函数，齐次化后会得到相应的齐次边界。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
常微分下的特殊Duhamel原理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
设
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{L}$
\end_inset

 为
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

的线性微分算子且 关于
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

的导数不超过
\begin_inset Formula $m-1$
\end_inset

 阶, 则非齐次方程的初值问题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
\mathcal{L}w=f\left(t\right)\\
w\mid_{t=0}=\ldots=\frac{d^{m-1}w}{dt^{m-1}}\mid_{t=0}=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
t>0\\
\\
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
的解为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
w\left(t\right)=\int_{0}^{t}f\left(\tau\right)z\left(t-\tau\right)d\tau
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
其中z满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
\mathcal{L}z=0\\
z\mid_{t=\tau}=\ldots=\frac{d^{m-2}z}{dt^{m-2}}\mid_{t=\tau}=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
t>0\\
\frac{\partial^{m-1}z}{\partial t^{m-1}}\mid_{t=\tau}=1
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
参考9.2.2
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
有界弦受迫振动问题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
来看看边值问题里面最难的问题之一：有界弦受迫振动问题。可以说是边值问题的大boss了，其难度不在于思路，而是过程非常繁复。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
u_{tt}=c^{2}u_{xx}+f\left(x,t\right)\\
u\left(x,0\right)=\varphi\left(x\right)\\
u_{t}\left(x,0\right)=\psi\left(x\right)\\
u\left(0,t\right)=u\left(l,t\right)=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
0<x<l,t>0\\
0<x<l\\
0<x<l\\
(Dirichlet\text{边\text{界}})
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在此先介绍一般思路：先叠加原理，把初值齐次化。再用分离变量法，得到特征方程，再去化有源为无源。这样做的好处是，只需要常微分下的特殊Duhamel原理，而非偏微分
的形式。处理ODE的有源问题当然比PDE简单地多。另外还有一个特殊武器：特解法。这个在后面也会简要提及。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
先由叠加原理，
\begin_inset Formula $u=w+v$
\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $w,v$
\end_inset

分别满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
w_{tt}=c^{2}w_{xx}+f\left(x,t\right)\\
w\left(x,0\right)=0\\
w_{t}\left(x,0\right)=0\\
w\left(0,t\right)=w\left(l,t\right)=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
0<x<l,t>0\\
0<x<l\\
0<x<l\\
(Dirichlet\text{边\text{界}})
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
和
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
v_{tt}=c^{2}v_{xx}\\
v\left(x,0\right)=\varphi\left(x\right)\\
v_{t}\left(x,0\right)=\psi\left(x\right)\\
v\left(0,t\right)=v\left(l,t\right)=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
0<x<l,t>0\\
0<x<l\\
0<x<l\\
(Dirichlet\text{边\text{界}})
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

我们已经知道（于10.1.1）：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
v=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}\left(\left(\frac{2}{l}\int_{0}^{l}\varphi\left(s\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}sds\right)cos\frac{cn\pi}{l}t+\left(\frac{2}{cn\pi}\int_{0}^{l}\psi\left(s\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}sds\right)sin\frac{cn\pi}{l}t\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于
\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

，我们不要直接Duhamel，有一个很巧妙的办法是，我们假设
\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

有分离解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
w=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}X_{n}\left(t\right)T_{n}\left(t\right)
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
希望这个
\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

满足
\begin_inset Formula $w_{tt}=c^{2}w_{xx}+f\left(x,t\right)$
\end_inset

，注意到边值是已经固定死的，我们先求出
\begin_inset Formula $X_{n}\left(t\right)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
X^{\prime\prime}+\lambda X=0\\
X\left(0\right)=X\left(l\right)=0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求出特征值
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{n}=\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}$
\end_inset

，特征函数为
\begin_inset Formula $X_{n}=sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x$
\end_inset

，由Strum-Liouville边值定理，函数系
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ X_{n}\right\} $
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $0<x<l$
\end_inset

上完备，然后我们看
\begin_inset Formula $T_{n}\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

需要满足怎么样的条件。要满足
\begin_inset Formula $w_{tt}=c^{2}w_{xx}+f\left(x,t\right)$
\end_inset

而
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
w_{tt}=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}T_{n}^{\prime\prime}\left(t\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x\\
w_{xx}=-\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}T_{n}\left(t\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
代入得到
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}T_{n}^{\prime\prime}\left(t\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x=-c^{2}\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}T_{n}\left(t\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x+f\left(x,t\right)
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}\left[T_{n}^{\prime\prime}\left(t\right)+c^{2}\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}T_{n}\left(t\right)\right]sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x=f\left(x,t\right)
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
那么实际上由Fourier展开，我们可以把
\begin_inset Formula $f\left(x,t\right)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $0<x<l$
\end_inset

上展开，因为
\begin_inset Formula $\text{函数系}\left\{ X_{n}\right\} $
\end_inset

完备，所以这是可行的，即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
f\left(x,t\right)=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}C_{n}\left(t\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其中
\begin_inset Formula $C_{n}$
\end_inset

满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
C_{n}\left(t\right)=\frac{\left(f,X_{n}\right)}{\left(X_{n},X_{n}\right)}=\frac{2}{l}\int_{0}^{l}f\left(s,t\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}sds=f_{n}\left(t\right)
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
再和（10.62）对比不难发现，只要让
\begin_inset Formula $T_{n}$
\end_inset

满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
T_{n}^{\prime\prime}\left(t\right)+c^{2}\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}T_{n}\left(t\right)=f_{n}\left(t\right)\\
T_{n}\left(0\right)=T_{n}^{\prime}\left(0\right)=0
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由常微分下的特殊Duhamel原理，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
T_{n}\left(t\right)=\int_{0}^{t}f\left(\tau\right)z_{n}\left(t-\tau\right)d\tau
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其中z满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
z_{n}^{\prime\prime}\left(t\right)+c^{2}\left(\frac{n\pi}{l}\right)^{2}z_{n}\left(t\right)=0\\
z_{n}\left(0\right)=0
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
t>0\\
z_{n}^{\prime}\left(0\right)=1
\end{array}\end{cases}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
z_{n}=\frac{l}{cn\pi}sin\frac{cn\pi}{l}t
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
于是
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
T_{n}\left(t\right)=\frac{l}{cn\pi}\int_{0}^{t}f_{n}\left(\tau\right)sin\frac{cn\pi}{l}\left(t-\tau\right)d\tau=\frac{l}{cn\pi}\int_{0}^{t}\left(\frac{2}{l}\int_{0}^{l}f\left(s,\tau\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}sds\right)sin\frac{cn\pi}{l}\left(t-\tau\right)d\tau
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
为了不看花眼，把变量s换成p，化简为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
T_{n}\left(t\right)=\frac{2}{cn\pi}\int_{0}^{t}\int_{0}^{l}f\left(p,\tau\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}p\cdot sin\frac{cn\pi}{l}\left(t-\tau\right)dpd\tau
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
于是得到
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
w=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}X_{n}\left(t\right)T_{n}\left(t\right)=\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}\left(\frac{2}{cn\pi}\int_{0}^{t}\int_{0}^{l}f\left(p,\tau\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}p\cdot sin\frac{cn\pi}{l}\left(t-\tau\right)dpd\tau\right)sin\frac{n\pi}{l}x
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
于是得到最终答案
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
