\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在8.1.2小节我们了解到在一维情况下，定义波动方程的能量为
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E\left(t\right)=\frac{1}{2}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}u_{t}^{2}+c^{2}u_{x}^{2}dx
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
自然而然地我们想到把它拓展到3维，此时有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E\left(t\right)=\frac{1}{2}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{3}}u_{t}^{2}+c^{2}\left|\nabla u\right|^{2}dx
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这样定义的能量到底有没有道理呢？我们来验证一下
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{dE}{dt}=\frac{1}{2}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{3}}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}\left(u_{t}^{2}+c^{2}\left|\nabla u\right|^{2}\right)dx
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
注意到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{1}{2}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}\left(u_{t}^{2}+c^{2}\left|\nabla u\right|^{2}\right)=u_{tt}u_{t}+c^{2}\underset{x,y,z}{\sum}u_{x}u_{xt}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
为了和我们的条件
\begin_inset Formula $u_{tt}=c^{2}\Delta u$
\end_inset

搭上关系，拆项有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{x}u_{xt}=\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\left(u_{x}u_{t}\right)-u_{xx}u_{t}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
代入到（12.4）得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
