如果我们假设
\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}$
\end_inset

满足
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underset{r\rightarrow+\infty}{lim}u_{t}=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
那么就有
